'''Tank 23''' was the [[Bacta tank/Legends|bacta tank]] in [[Ward 114]] on the [[Mercy (hospital ship)|''Mercy'']], where [[Kyle Katarn]] was healed after being injured on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. Unlike other tanks in the ward, nobody had hanged medals or notes on its surface. The cupboard attached to it contained Kyle's [[Clothing/Legends|clothes]], [[Boot/Legends|boots]], [[Bryar pistol/Legends|Bryar pistol]], [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|wallet]], a [[holocube]] recording with [[Morgan Katarn|his father]], a 3-D snapshot of [[Jan Ors]], and a [[Hologram disc/Legends|holodisk]] acquired from [[8t88/Legends|8t88]].

[[Jan Ors]] visited Katarn while he was there, about 12 [[Standard hour/Legends|hours]] after their arrival. Curious about Katarn's [[Mission to Nar Shaddaa (5 ABY)|business on Nar Shaddaa]], and why that holodisk was so important for him, she browsed among his belongings and took the disk before returning them in the cupboard. She realised that her feelings were mutual when she discovered her snapshot in his things.<ref name="Dark Forces: Rebel Agent">''[[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent]]''</ref>

